what you inspired in me

12:21.241 --> 12:23.341
30 years ago.

12:23.377 --> 12:25.744
I'm going to hurt your brain...
[laughter]

12:25.779 --> 12:28.313
Using these four cards
and four coins

12:28.348 --> 12:32.450
in an original routine I call
The Ultimate Matrix.

