the mysterious Asian sounds.

14:29.236 --> 14:31.636
[sharp breathy exhalations]

14:31.672 --> 14:34.305
There's the first one.
[applause]

14:34.341 --> 14:37.142
I'll do it again.

14:37.177 --> 14:39.010
[sharp breathy exhalations]

14:39.046 --> 14:40.845
And that makes three.

14:40.881 --> 14:45.583
The next one--no hands,
just because I can.

14:45.619 --> 14:47.152
[breathes out]

14:47.187 --> 14:50.722
Vanishes here,
reappears in the corner.

14:50.757 --> 14:54.526
And I'm in beast mode.
[applause]

14:56.296 --> 14:59.164
That's what it looks like
using four cards for cover.

14:59.199 --> 15:01.366
This time, no cards.

15:01.401 --> 15:03.635
Just my bare hands
and a dose of honesty.

15:03.670 --> 15:05.670
[laughter]
I've been performing magic

15:05.706 --> 15:07.238
since I was eight years old,

15:07.274 --> 15:10.909
and it took me 12 years
to create this act.

15:10.944 --> 15:14.345
So for me, this is not
just a magic trick.

15:14.381 --> 15:16.448
This is something far deeper,

15:16.483 --> 15:19.951
and a thousand times
more savage.

15:19.986 --> 15:23.788
A work of terrifying beauty
that has been growing

15:23.824 --> 15:27.092
all my life,
like an uncontrollable weed

15:27.127 --> 15:31.663
in the garden of my mind.
[applause]

15:31.698 --> 15:35.166
I have crossed oceans of time
and vast empires

15:35.202 --> 15:38.803
to be here today, so I take
the honor of performing here

15:38.839 --> 15:40.271
very seriously.

15:40.307 --> 15:42.707
The amount of mental energy
I've invested

15:42.743 --> 15:46.578
in creating this act
could demolish planets.

15:46.613 --> 15:49.814
This is the most epic monologue
in the history of magic.

15:49.850 --> 15:51.716
For I am here...
[laughter]

15:51.752 --> 15:54.352
To inflict
psychological damage,

15:54.387 --> 15:56.221
and that means...

15:56.256 --> 16:00.325
We're not done yet.
[applause]

16:07.234 --> 16:10.335
You've now seen the devastation
I can generate using two hands.

16:10.370 --> 16:11.903
Let's take this
to the next level.

16:11.938 --> 16:14.539
I'll do it again with just...

16:14.574 --> 16:16.407
One hand.

16:16.443 --> 16:18.076
You can ask any magician
around the world

16:18.111 --> 16:20.278
about performing
an illusion this clean,

16:20.313 --> 16:22.113
