17:10.497 --> 17:12.864
[cheering and applause]

17:12.898 --> 17:15.200
You would not believe
how epic this feels!

17:15.234 --> 17:18.703
My heart is pounding,
and I can feel the adrenaline

17:18.738 --> 17:21.271
coursing through my veins.

17:21.308 --> 17:23.141
I'd like to thank each
and every one of you

17:23.175 --> 17:24.742
for sharing this moment
with me,

17:24.778 --> 17:27.878
because just being here
was a dream come true.

17:27.914 --> 17:30.682
So for everyone watching:
if you have a dream,

17:30.717 --> 17:33.318
never give up believing
in your dream,

17:33.353 --> 17:36.054
living your dream,
and doing something every day

17:36.089 --> 17:38.156
to make that dream happen.

17:38.191 --> 17:40.225
But remember one thing.

17:40.260 --> 17:42.393
No matter who you are,

17:42.429 --> 17:44.762
no matter how hard you work,

17:44.798 --> 17:47.565
or how good you think you are
at what you do,

17:47.601 --> 17:52.370
there will always be an Asian
who takes it to the next level.

17:52.405 --> 17:53.404
[laughter,
cheering and applause]

17:53.440 --> 17:55.406
Yeah!
I'm Ryan Hayashi,

17:55.442 --> 17:57.041
